nodes.text: The Karthakk Sector Force was a Rebel Alliance Sector Force, assigned to the Karthakk sector during the Galactic Civil War. Like most of the other Sector Forces, it was created from a local resistance movement: the Karthakk resistance. This Sector Force was known to be able to support respectable fleets and armies from its own resources.
